headline: Netanyahu: Attempt to pin extremist actions on me is immoral
description: Finance Minister Benjamin Netanyahu responded to attacks made on him by Labor MKs today.    “I suggest the Labor party concentrates on rebuilding its own wreckage, rather than what is happening in the Likud," said Netanyahu. "The attempt to make me responsible for what criminal daydreamers are doing is immoral.” (Diana Bahur-Nir)
articleBody: Finance Minister Benjamin Netanyahu responded to attacks made on him by Labor MKs today.    “I suggest the Labor party concentrates on rebuilding its own wreckage, rather than what is happening in the Likud," said Netanyahu. "The attempt to make me responsible for what criminal daydreamers are doing is immoral.” (Diana Bahur-Nir)
title:
בסטודיו של מותג האופנה אלף 
אלף: "זו זוגיות בתוך עיצוב"
